Class XmlItemInfoList

    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.perftools.common.XmlItemInfoList

  • public class XmlItemInfoList
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds a list of items from an XML file. This may be used by applications to determine what items to open when starting a session.
